nticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"role":"collection"}}}